### Stream truncated for artifact (~70+ entries captured; on-device cadence
### was unbroken until devicectl --console attach was stopped). Multiple
### chat-level rate-limit suppressions occurred; the original radio-level
### cadence on the iPhone was uninterrupted. CoreBluetooth
### CBCentralManagerScanOptionAllowDuplicatesKey was active, so each
### radio packet triggered a delegate call — observed ~10 callbacks/sec
### across the two-Android population.
###
### rssi=127 is the CoreBluetooth sentinel for "unknown RSSI" returned
### when the radio sample is unavailable; treat as missing, not as
### in-range.
